Package GUI

Class MainWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • GUI.MainWindow
  • public class MainWindow
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    riley This is the main window class, which is responsible for containing the full window that the user sees. It depends on the Simulation, controller box, and grapher class to function. it essentially manages the controllers interaction with the aforementioned classes. Use this class as a instance var for the controller main class.
